## Implémentation Python

```{.python code-line-numbers="|1|6|9"}
def mth_newton(f, f_p, x0, eps=1e-8, max_iter=100):
    x = x0
    for i in range():
        fx = f(x)
        if abs(fx) < eps:
            return x
        fpx = f_p(x)
        if fpx == 0:
            break
        x -= fx / fpx
    return x
```


